commit 0610f54fb7b9465756c825010b507074a920c28c
Author: igs-jiunchiwang <jiunchiwang@igs.com.tw>
Date:   Fri Jun 19 18:11:15 2026 +0800

    refactor: unify reply parse_mode to HTML and dedupe dispatch logic

    Specialist proxy replies and other user-facing replies now render via
    markdownToHtml() with parse_mode "HTML" (matching the main agent),
    falling back to tag-stripped plain text on HTML parse errors, replacing
    the previous parse_mode "Markdown". Internal/command UI messages keep
    Markdown.

    Consolidate three duplicated specialist-proxy implementations (inline in
    index.ts and run-prompt.ts, plus the extracted-but-unused function in
    relay.ts) into a single handleSpecialistProxy(), parameterized by an
    optional startTarget to cover both the initial-activation and
    continuation paths.

    Consolidate the relay / parallel / headless delegate dispatch logic into
    the shared dispatchRelayVisible(), dispatchParallelDelegates(), and
    dispatchRelayHeadless() in relay.ts; run-prompt.ts now calls them instead
    of holding its own inline copies. The >=2-specialist cross-check guidance
    is preserved.

    Remove imports orphaned by the deletions across all three files.

    Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>

